-- TelecomDaily Survey Says 52% of Russians Abroad Use Cell Roaming
-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 2012-06-15T04:46:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-15/telecomdaily-survey-says-52-of-russians-abroad-use-cell-roaming.html
More than half of Russians
travelling outside their country use international roaming
services on their cellphones, TelecomDaily reported yesterday,
citing a survey.  Of 1,953 passengers surveyed in airports in Moscow and  St.
Petersburg  earlier this month, 52 percent said they used a
roaming service while abroad, the Russian telecoms news service
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Jordan in Moscow at 
